Class WrappedClock

java.lang.Object

      org.middleheaven.quantity.time.clocks.WrappedClock
Direct Known Subclasses:
AlarmClock, SpeedyClock, TimeContextClock, TimeZoneClock
public abstract class WrappedClock
extends Clock

Encapsulates another Clock implementation in order to change the original clock behaviour or derive the new Clock properties from the encapsulated clock.
